{"tid":1694452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢間鋪頭係咪食人血饅頭食滯左？","createTime":"2019-11-05T07:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T13:44:42.000Z","uid":141243,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2d1b33d7a2a379ef5380ba8dfad7272faa88b9a6","tid":1694452,"uid":141243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"碌曬成個post都冇話賣完pepe會捐錢<br />\n只係話捐左少少買飯券<br />\n又話啲電話殼會捐部分收益出去<br />\n但你最後又唔講自己捐咗幾多<br />\n<br />\n唔係話賣pepe就抵屌<br />\n講真明買明賣係無問題嘅<br />\n但可唔可以唔好成日打住發夢嘅旗號嚟賣嘢<br />\n打句香港加油啲錢又袋袋平安<br />\n仲要你pepe一睇就知係淘寶嘢<br />\n自己加個口罩黑衫就當係原創<br />\n<br />\n衰啲講句我真係寧願你悶聲發大財<br />\n都唔好喺度扮曬關心香港<br />\n仲要佢自己個IG仲要成日po自己去玩嘅相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現補下佢ig圖<br />\n買唔買你自己諗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzOOnZN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzOOnZN.png&h=b50b8024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講左幾撚耐罷金拱門<br />\n但你買佢飯券都算<br />\n呢度加撚埋都唔知有冇200<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/145MT63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F145MT63.png&h=aefa40b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n帶pepe出去發夢<br />\n掛係書包博比人拉？？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講真如果你只係賣pepe我話知你<br />\n但唔該你唔好以香港人自稱去整啲黑衫黑口罩去呃啲黃絲錢<br />\n你如果唔知咩叫人血饅頭唔該你去讀魯迅《藥》<br />\n你依家就同入面嘅人一樣咁撚仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308b1a62079ab58b3da82ddf17b98e420d223686","tid":1694452,"uid":199926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:23:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OzEervM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzEervM.png&h=f57b273f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約定你11月6 Sogo崇光百貨感謝祭 下午三點銅鑼灣見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691137</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},